strings: <voice_0x01001D21><se_high>Princess Medea: I, I still can't quite believe that you're the son of King Clavius's brother.

<voice_0x01001D22><se_high>Princess Medea: That makes you Prince Charmles's cousin,
doesn't it?

<voice_0x01001D23><se_high>Princess Medea: .........
Fate can be so cruel.

<voice_0x01001D24><se_high>Princess Medea: ...Sorry, I shouldn't have said that.
It's been decided now.
There's nothing to be done about it.
<voice_0x01001D27><se_high>Princess Medea: Oh yes! What about Munchie? Can you believe that little mouse was really Chen Mui all along?
<voice_0x01001D28><se_high>Princess Medea: Did you have any idea?
<voice_0x01001D29><se_high>Princess Medea: You know, all those years ago when I first found you in the forest, it was Munchie that led me to you.
<voice_0x01001D2A><se_high>Princess Medea: To think that Chen Mui has been watching over you all this time <endash> and from your own coat pocket, no less!
